        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You are trained with @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Composite Longbow]{Composite Longbows}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Composite Shortbow]{Composite Shortbows}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Glaive]{Glaives}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Longbow]{Longbows}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Longsword]{Longswords}, and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Shortbow]{Shortbows}.</p>\n<p>In addition, you gain access to all uncommon hobgoblin weapons. For the purpose of determining your proficiency, martial hobgoblin weapons are simple weapons and advanced hobgoblin weapons are martial weapons.</p>"
